Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:39.91,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}谎话连篇的你 爱哭鼻子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.96,0:00:45.81,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么进展得不顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:51.78,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}精心打扮的头发 光彩夺目的指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:57.68,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你却都没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:04.81,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}love 并非悲伤的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:09.81,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}干涩的眼睛只是有些刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:16.07,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水滚落不停 I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:24.31,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:29.29,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理解那炽热的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.87,0:01:36.48,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论在哪里 都彼此相连
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:41.31,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}连你并不可爱的哭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:43.33,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我也深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天突然要给店里帮忙就不能去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天出去逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我要跟小水他们去吃自助蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起时又没钱又不喜欢我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只喝果味牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去吃自助蛋糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自助蛋糕？ 啊上周去过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七没去呀 她没什么钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她羡慕的话下次一起去怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 上哪去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不着竹内呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了就明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在跟踪我女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 圣诞礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 竹内君的话就知道矢野喜欢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你陪我去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你选的东西 不管什么他都开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别那么说 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不了啦 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你自己选的东西他绝对会更开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 可是我品味不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你收到矢野的礼物时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野托你朋友选的你喜欢的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和矢野自己发着愁 为你选的你不感兴趣的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到哪个更高兴？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野自己选的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 是来买礼物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明明没什么钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 听说要给店里帮忙就找不到他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年底嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了 出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着袋子 好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天跟踪完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 会露馅儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心你是不是买好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 买完了呀 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这点事 回见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好不容易见到喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 我真有事先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听匡史说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年出事故的孩子 那是你女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你一次都没去上过坟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了她 而是为了你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买上她喜欢的花 带些清水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧元晴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候也该哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个笨女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨女人也会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔也晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说男生 认真点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别打雪仗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天矢野一次都没看我 错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉气呼呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂好无聊的 别装了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别扯淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能还不了解矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞礼物 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我没有恶意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 你还活着嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好难过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个那个 我犹豫了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过喜欢帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你没有带毛球的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可颜色我犹豫了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是可是你不喜欢的话我就去换
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合适
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:08:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我暂时也得喝果味牛奶了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总哭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是多愁善感呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然别人总说伤心的时候再哭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流泪的话 开心的眼泪比悲伤的眼泪好得多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从遇到矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得好像变得爱哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 数1课本落在柜子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 那回去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能不去 还有一堆作业呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我去下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次在楼梯摔倒时 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你别再帮我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想欠人情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那么讨厌我一开始就别接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明是为了向姐姐复仇才利用我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事没有任何理由和意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我加上特别的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 你为什么哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了？ 矢野哭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有那种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 你为什么哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是在山本同学面前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 又找你商量 明明是寒假
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我也有点在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我有点难以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么他会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:12:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很久前就认识他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一次都没哭过 也没让人看到过软弱的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你原来也这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可作为一个人 可能也有谁都不知道的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都觉得矢野不是这种类型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本同学和矢野中学时有过什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常觉得他们两个很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 不是挺平常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本本来就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着有些别扭那还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少和奈奈有些关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈 为什么搭原来男友的车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么做出背叛矢野的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来的男友那么有魅力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵 根本没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人最差了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙都说 怎么跟那种男人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是让她带着伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤 为什么和那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙也都说矢野 怎么跟那种笨女人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱就是那么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 只有当事人明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 这么冷还叫你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟矢野两个人也够笨的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都胡闹 还牵连别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会 我觉得不笨就不是真的情侣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内君在他们交往时也想过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么跟那种笨女人交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他让人发火 像个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛离不开她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:13:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从始至终
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又坐第一排啊 换坐运气好差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你看那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 最糟的组合了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐换得最糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂且不能忘东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘带课本时就和我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借同桌的看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便在我睡着了要被点名的时候叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我坐山本旁边可是第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从初一到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时也不跟她借课本看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我一次都没忘过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0}初中的时候 你和山本同学发生过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一想到有奈奈纠缠就变得懦弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 上次的礼物是和竹内一起买的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么骗我说和小水吃自助蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 你说骗人… 我只想给你个惊喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我知道 也别骗我和别的男人见面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应我 不要背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天从哪页开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了吗 给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐山本旁边不难受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一句话都不说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她上次冲我瞪眼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好开口借课本看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧换坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我看看课本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不清的放中间好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开45页
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么预习了10页
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在家没别的事做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事干就学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 想要钱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这么没梦想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说梦想我有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等有了很多钱 去迪斯尼乐园约会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野你有钱了 想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我不要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要钱的 我想要爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然说想要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 对啊 是爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的话多少我都给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那周六我妈不在 来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱对矢野来说就是H啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野啊 那周六能来我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 你妈不在么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:17:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脑子里只有那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊矢野 不能回应你的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 不是没钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的全部财产
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要矢野对我笑就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事还是别管的好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一直对矢野微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 忘带生物了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好容易拿回去好像就忘带回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜啊 要借我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 借我看看 山本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本同学借课本给你真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 周日来我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周日的话你可能觉得合适
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸妈出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家不大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 蒙我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)}你说什么呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和你的房间比很小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 书包放那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野在我房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有些 感动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家住哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住柳町
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离这不近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,444)\fs22}不会 坐公车不用换车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和矢野在说话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,444)\fs22}长得挺帅呀 很受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲 品评中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,444)\fs22}啊 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊真是的 越来越觉得对不住矢野了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,444)\fs22}你父亲做什么工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做房地产相关 那个 矢野家很大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 嗯 你什么时候去打扰过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 那房子没看上去那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你没进去过 可我的房间只有4叠半呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 放张CD吧 你听什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和在外面完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来拯救一下这沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也不干的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你妈像是不敲门就直接进的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没礼貌啊 才不会那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 这是疼爱你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常非常喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你交往 就越来越发现出原来不知道的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:21:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说 比原来想的笨一点呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些孩子气呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样 他抚摸着头发
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就越来越喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嫉妒山本同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起知道我不了解的矢野的山本同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和矢野距离最近 想知道矢野的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想 是任性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.40,0:22:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次说“没有隐瞒”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以后绝对再不说谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以矢野也别说谎好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算肯定是我胡思乱想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和山本同学发生过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:22:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我为什么 和你的理由一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是没有隐瞒吗 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 不回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:42.20,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}季節が少し動いた気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.70,0:23:50.80,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}陽射しも短く　いつかずれて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:59.20,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}二人のバスは　変わらない街
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:06.90,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}走っていること　ホッとしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.90,0:24:16.40,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}窓の外　いつもみたいに見てるあなた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.70,0:24:27.80,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そしてわたしも真似をしている いつもみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.00,0:24:36.70,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ねぇ　ふたりは　おなじなのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.50,0:24:40.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}行きたい場所は？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.30,0:24:44.70,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}黙っていたって　いいんだよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.70,0:24:54.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ねぇ　ふたりは　同じなのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.30,0:24:57.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いとしい気持ち……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.20,0:25:03.60,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの視線は　いま、見えなくて……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:42.20,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我感到季节略微变换
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.70,0:23:50.80,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}阳光不知在何时变短
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:59.20,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要公交车仍在那街道行驶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:06.90,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}两人就把心放宽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.90,0:24:16.40,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你总是一如既往地望向窗外
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.70,0:24:27.80,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}于是我也学着你 一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.00,0:24:36.70,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喂 我们两个是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.50,0:24:40.00,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}要去的地方是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.30,0:24:44.70,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}沉默不语 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.70,0:24:54.00,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喂 我们两个是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.30,0:24:57.00,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}爱恋的感觉是一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.20,0:25:03.60,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的视线 如今我看不见…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.30,0:25:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本同学喜欢矢野吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.90,0:25:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本喜欢我还是讨厌我都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.30,0:25:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我没关系 我也没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.00,0:25:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了 那天你们一起回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.00,0:25:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 跟她妹妹在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.60,0:25:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我旁边啊 高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.10,0:25:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以做的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.90,0:25:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
